Definition: a message expressing a belief about something
Example: the expression of a belief that is held with confidence but not substantiated by positive knowledge or proof; his opinions appeared frequently on the editorial page
Synonyms: verb, communication, opine, view, cognition, message, a, expressing, belief, about, something, the, expression, of, that, is, held, with, confidence, but, not, substantiated, by, positive, knowledge, or, proof, his, opinions, appeared, frequently, on, editorial, page
Category: noun.communication
